types of surgeries may be performed.  
All inmates have a full medical control 
while entering in the penitentiary 
establishment. The medical examination is 
also mandatory when inmate is transferred 
from one penitentiary establishment to 
another before allocation to the concrete 
cell.  
 
<b><i>Non-governmental sources:</i></b>  In certain 
establishments prisoners reportedly 
complain about the food ration and quality 
of meal. 
