police stations, Criminal 
Investigation Departments 
(CIDs), border guard stations 
and migration detention cetres 
were very poor throughout the 
country.  
 
The conditions of detention were 
</p>
<p><b>Government: </b>Prison administration take 
care of the strict observance of hygiene 
rules and the maintenance of facilities, 
always in compliance with personal hygiene 
and sanitation rules governing the operation 
of detention facilities, as well as the relevant 
instructions of the Ministry of Justice, 
Transparency and Human Rights.  
