<p><b>Impunity</b>  <b> </b> gg. Establish accessible and effective complaints mechanisms in <i>all 
</i>places of detention. At a minimum, there should be a mechanism to 
allow for complaints of torture and ill-treatment, to be promptly and 
thoroughly investigated by an independent authority and those 
responsible held accountable including by disciplinary and penal 
measures as appropriate. Furthermore, complainants must be protected 
from reprisals. 
