in the country&#8216;s detention facilities was 
</p>
<p>established. This register records the 
incident, the name of the doctor who 
conducted the search, justification of the 
search, the date and time of the search and 
explicit reference to the prosecutor&#8216;s order, 
</p>
<p>on the basis of which it was conducted. 
