<p><b>Juveniles</b>  <b> </b> jj. Detention for unaccompanied minors should be a last resort 
measure. In order to ensure adequate protection to juveniles, the 
Ministry of Health and the Ministry of Interior should cooperate 
closely to ensure that they are placed in separate reception centres. 
