ensures that any act of violence against 
children will be punished by law. The 
National Action Plan for the Eradication 
of Violence against Children of 2006, the 
&#8213;Stop Violence Against Children&#8214; 
campaign and various pilot projects 
conducted by Friendly Schools for 
Children in several regions further 
strengthened the implementation of the 
law. 
</p>
