<p>77. All allegations of torture 
and ill-treatment should be 
promptly and thoroughly 
investigated ex-officio by an 
independent authority with no 
connection to the authority 
investigating or prosecuting 
the case against the alleged 
</p>
<p>There was a lack of adequate 
mechanisms to investigate 
