<p>considered to ensure timely and fair 
investigation of alleged torture by services 
not belonging to law enforcement agencies, 
and to relieve them of their official duties 
for the duration of the investigation and 
court proceedings (Action Plan of the 
Government of the Republic of Kazakhstan 
for 2009-2012 to implement the 
