the suspect may be forced to waive his right 
to a lawyer unless the participation of the 
lawyer is mandatory. Third, Kazakh 
authorities can use so-called &#8213;pocket&#8214; 
advocates appointed by the investigator, 
who cannot are not independent lawyers 
