caused as a result of unlawful acts of the 
body leading or carrying out criminal 
proceedings; however the list of unlawful 
acts does not include torture or ill-treatment. 
Nonetheless, a resolution of the Supreme 
Court of 9 July 1999 (No. 7) on the practical 
application of the legislation on the 
