- Compulsory placement in a medical 
institution of a person not in pretrial 
detention for the performance of a judicial-
medical expert evaluation is allowed 
pursuant to a court decision or on the basis 
of a sanction by the procurator. No 
maximum period for such treatment is 
stipulated by the law, the process lacks 
transparency and there appears to be no 
possibility to appeal such a decision.  
 
<b>Government:</b> Under article 91 of the Code 
on Public Health and system of health 
