<p>there are no political appointees. 
Furthermore, section 30 of the draft 
bill is extremely concerning as it 
allows for the powers of the NHRC to 
be delegated to the Government of 
Nepal or to &#8213;any agency or institution 
or any person&#8214;.  
 
