Drochia and Cahul. 
 
<b>Non-governmental sources:</b> Moldova is a 
source and, to a lesser extent, a transit and 
destination country for trafficking in women, 
men and children for purposes of forced 
prostitution, begging and forced labour. The 
small breakaway region of Transnistria in 
eastern Moldova is outside the central 
Government&#8216;s control and remained a source of 
</p>
