<p><i>reporting period  
</i></p>
<p>Section 18 (Civil and Political 
Rights) of the NHRAP, proposes 
several prioritized measures to 
ensure compliance with minimum 
standards for the treatment of 
prisoners and will address issues 
including deficiencies in prison 
conditions and overcrowding.  
 
<b><i>Non-governmental sources:</i></b>  There 
