under article 235 of the Criminal Code. During the 
inspection carried out by the organs of procuracy in 
2009 and in the period of 9 months in 2010, 13 criminal 
cases were initiated in relation to 20 employees of law 
enforcement bodies who were subsequently suspended 
from their duties. 
